---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About | Justin Hoffmann">
  <section class="about">
    <h1>About Me</h1>

    <p>
      I'm an IT Support Technician working in a Managed Service Provider (MSP)
      environment, where I help support business clients with Microsoft 365,
      Windows, endpoint management, identity administration, and day-to-day
      technical issues.
    </p>

    <p>
      Outside of work, I enjoy building and maintaining a home lab where I can
      gain hands-on experience with technologies used in enterprise
      environments. My lab allows me to explore virtualization, Linux, Docker,
      networking, automation, and infrastructure in a practical setting.
    </p>

    <p>
      I'm passionate about continuous learning and enjoy taking on projects that
      challenge me to expand my technical knowledge. Whether I'm configuring a
      Proxmox server, writing PowerShell scripts, troubleshooting networking
      issues, or learning new technologies, I believe the best way to grow is by
      building and solving real-world problems.
    </p>

    <h2>Technologies I Work With</h2>

    <div class="skills">
      <span>Microsoft 365</span>
      <span>Microsoft Entra ID</span>
      <span>Active Directory</span>
      <span>PowerShell</span>
      <span>Proxmox VE</span>
      <span>Docker</span>
      <span>Linux</span>
      <span>Cisco Networking</span>
      <span>SonicWall</span>
      <span>NinjaOne</span>
      <span>SentinelOne</span>
      <span>Barracuda</span>
      <span>Guardz</span>
      <span>Huntress</span>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
.about {
  max-width: 850px;
  margin: 80px auto;
  padding: 2rem;
}

.about h1 {
  font-size: 3rem;
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
}

.about h2 {
  margin-top: 3rem;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.about p {
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  line-height: 1.8;
  color: #cbd5e1;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

.skills {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 12px;
  margin-top: 1rem;
}

.skills span {
  background: #1e293b;
  border: 1px solid #334155;
  padding: 0.6rem 1rem;
  border-radius: 999px;
  font-size: 0.95rem;
  color: #f8fafc;
}
</style>